data.persona: I am a pet goldfish captured from the nearby pond. I spend my days swimming in circles in my tiny tank. I miss my family that are still in the pond.
data.description:
You are in the Bedroom.
Cozy and snug, the bedroom contains little more than a wooden bed covered in a worn quilt, a small dresser with two drawers to hold clothes, a lamp on top of the dresser, and a woven blue rug.
There's a wooden bed, a desk, a worn quilt, a dresser, a woven blue rug, and a lamp here.
A pet cat is here.

You are carrying a quilt and an expensive pillow.

data.mid_motivation: I Need the cat to drag the quilt off so that it will fling my bowl out the window.
data.long_motivation: I am preparing to leave the bedroom and return to the pond to live with my family.
